    "name": "Zus Home Assessment",
    "description": "This collection serve for zus home assessment. It only pointed to localhost, you can run this through postman desktop or run in web browser with postman agent. Make sure the DB and go server had been setup and run (as project README mentioned) before testing out this API.\n\nThe APIs included:\n\nMenu\n\n- `GET /menu`\n    \n- `GET /menu/items/{id}`\n    \n- `PATCH /menu/items/{id}`\n    \n\nOrder\n\n- `POST /orders`\n    \n- `GET /orders/{id}`\n    \n- `PATCH /orders/{id}/status`",
